_sText:
de_beerhouse is a port of the de_beerhouse from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

de_beerhouse map set in a quaint country beergarden.

Counter-Terrorists:

We're being deployed from the back of the beer garden. Let's stop those terrorists from causing too much damage!

Terrorists:

We'll rush in from the parking lot. A squad of FBI agents is hot on our tail, so let's get in, and get out!

Other Notes: There is one bombsite in this mission.
